01:01:40.000 --> 01:01:55.000
As we said, the same option of CRM, for example, is a tactic. As a continuation of the CRM concept, we can consider the COV approach. What can we do here?

01:01:55.000 --> 01:02:10.000
In the CRM option, we started to divide our clients by certain principles and build an individual approach, that is, to increase the quality of individual communications. In the COV option, we try to determine how much money the client brings us.

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:30.000
We can calculate the profitability of a particular client, the speed of his appeal to us, frequency, regularity, and so on, and calculate how profitable he is for us. We can use the same BC, XY for this analysis, but the essence is not important.

01:02:30.000 --> 01:02:47.000
