01:12:21.000 --> 01:12:34.000
Therefore, an effective control system is a key issue that must be solved before we can say, yes, we have a plan, and I am ready to implement it.

01:12:34.000 --> 01:12:46.000
What is the specificity of strategic marketing? First of all, we can approach the formation of this marketing plan in different ways.

01:12:46.000 --> 01:13:05.000
A fairly common option is to form strategic marketing events based on the life cycle of a company or product on the market. This is a common approach, it is simple, understandable, although not fully valid.

01:13:05.000 --> 01:13:29.000
As an option, we can develop an intensive marketing strategy. For example, if we are in the first phase of the life cycle, our task is to invest actively and wait for profit to reinvest it in the market.

01:13:30.000 --> 01:13:48.000
We can take a different position and try to choose a strategy of penetration, when we stimulate the return of the profit, while waiting for someone to come to us.

01:13:48.000 --> 01:14:08.000
We can take a strategy of wide penetration, when we try to cover the market, and as a result, our investments in advertising and promotion will be much higher.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:26.000
We can take a passive position and not take risks. If, for example, the last phase of the life cycle is in the middle of a deadlock, it is logical to sit and wait for a client without investing money.

01:14:26.000 --> 01:14:42.000
We can build our strategy based not only on the life cycle, but also on other parameters, for example, the market we are in. The market can be global or local, there are quite a variety of options.

01:14:42.000 --> 01:15:05.000
